dct_title_s: A topographical map of the Monmouth Shore with the interior from Metuchen to Lakewood : from original surveys and levelings based on the triangulation of the U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contour lines and spot heights. Contour interval 10 feet. Depths shown by soundings and isolines. At top margin: Geological Survey of New Jersey. Atlas sheet No. 9 (Monmouth Shore).
dct_publisher_sm: [Trenton, N.J.] : The Survey, 1897 (N.Y. : Julius Bien & Co.)
